data.description: This delightful residence boasts three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, centrally located in the heart of Buffalo Grove. The kitchen and living room on the main level feature vaulted ceilings and plenty of windows, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. Upstairs, you'll find three bedrooms, each equipped with generous closet space and organizers, along with a full hallway bathroom. The lower level offers a spacious family room, an additional full bathroom, a large utility/laundry room, and a meticulously maintained crawl space, with an exit leading to the backyard. Outside, the property showcases a fantastic backyard, complete with a 1.5-car detached garage, a concrete patio, and an additional storage shed with electricity, enhancing the home's appeal both inside and out. This split-level home is located on a family-friendly, tree-lined street, offering close proximity to schools, parks, restaurants, public transit, shopping, and all the amenities Buffalo Grove has to offer, including Kilmer, Cooper, and Buffalo Grove High School.
